    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">
        <strong>07 February 1940</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">Volume 357</div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
        <div class="container">
            <div id="debateContent">
                <div class="highlightedSearchTerms"></div>
                <div class="content-container">


<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-4fb83ef9-9e40-459f-9fb0-c865dde079aa'>
            
<p class="">25.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-1b331b79-0f16-4b7d-88e4-0b1defdd2115">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-1b331b79-0f16-4b7d-88e4-0b1defdd2115">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-1b331b79-0f16-4b7d-88e4-0b1defdd2115">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-1b331b79-0f16-4b7d-88e4-0b1defdd2115">
                 Mr. Shinwell 
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-1b331b79-0f16-4b7d-88e4-0b1defdd2115" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-02-07/debates/a1154570-b9d4-4f6d-bacb-02914b0941f4/MerchantShipbuildingAndRepairs#contribution-1b331b79-0f16-4b7d-88e4-0b1defdd2115">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the First Lord of the Admiralty whether vessels for the merchant navy, built under the direction of his Department, will, on completion, <span id="197" class="column-number" data-column-number="197"></span> be managed by private firms or the Ministry of Shipping; and whether any of the vessels now building for private owners will be transferred to the Government?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-1b331b79-0f16-4b7d-88e4-0b1defdd2115" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-02-07/debates/a1154570-b9d4-4f6d-bacb-02914b0941f4/MerchantShipbuildingAndRepairs#contribution-1b331b79-0f16-4b7d-88e4-0b1defdd2115">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-4b9ec5ee-a137-41c5-b1e3-23da05725d0d">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-4b9ec5ee-a137-41c5-b1e3-23da05725d0d">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-4b9ec5ee-a137-41c5-b1e3-23da05725d0d">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-4b9ec5ee-a137-41c5-b1e3-23da05725d0d">
                Mr. Churchill
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-4b9ec5ee-a137-41c5-b1e3-23da05725d0d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-02-07/debates/a1154570-b9d4-4f6d-bacb-02914b0941f4/MerchantShipbuildingAndRepairs#contribution-4b9ec5ee-a137-41c5-b1e3-23da05725d0d">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Merchant ships built by the Admiralty will be delivered to the Ministry of Shipping, who will make arrangements for their management. Vessels now building for private owners will not, so far as can at present be foreseen, be transferred to Government ownership but will be subject to requisition or other control by the Minister of Shipping.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-4b9ec5ee-a137-41c5-b1e3-23da05725d0d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-02-07/debates/a1154570-b9d4-4f6d-bacb-02914b0941f4/MerchantShipbuildingAndRepairs#contribution-4b9ec5ee-a137-41c5-b1e3-23da05725d0d">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-ceb87710-83b5-4ca3-8e0e-9e5c36365019">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-ceb87710-83b5-4ca3-8e0e-9e5c36365019">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-ceb87710-83b5-4ca3-8e0e-9e5c36365019">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-ceb87710-83b5-4ca3-8e0e-9e5c36365019">
                Mr. Shinwell
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-ceb87710-83b5-4ca3-8e0e-9e5c36365019" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-02-07/debates/a1154570-b9d4-4f6d-bacb-02914b0941f4/MerchantShipbuildingAndRepairs#contribution-ceb87710-83b5-4ca3-8e0e-9e5c36365019">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">So far as tonnage under the control of the right hon. Gentleman is concerned, I take it that there will be no allocation to private firms, but that the ownership will be vested in the Ministry of Shipping?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-ceb87710-83b5-4ca3-8e0e-9e5c36365019" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-02-07/debates/a1154570-b9d4-4f6d-bacb-02914b0941f4/MerchantShipbuildingAndRepairs#contribution-ceb87710-83b5-4ca3-8e0e-9e5c36365019">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-8fb163a3-9c07-4831-9ec3-92189d5fe629">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-8fb163a3-9c07-4831-9ec3-92189d5fe629">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-8fb163a3-9c07-4831-9ec3-92189d5fe629">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-8fb163a3-9c07-4831-9ec3-92189d5fe629">
                Mr. Churchill
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-8fb163a3-9c07-4831-9ec3-92189d5fe629" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-02-07/debates/a1154570-b9d4-4f6d-bacb-02914b0941f4/MerchantShipbuildingAndRepairs#contribution-8fb163a3-9c07-4831-9ec3-92189d5fe629">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">We build for the Ministry of Shipping and we transfer the ships when built to the Ministry, and they arrange what the future of these ships is to be.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-8fb163a3-9c07-4831-9ec3-92189d5fe629" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-02-07/debates/a1154570-b9d4-4f6d-bacb-02914b0941f4/MerchantShipbuildingAndRepairs#contribution-8fb163a3-9c07-4831-9ec3-92189d5fe629">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-8db39b31-fa63-4f86-ac4c-b1a9e6d6063d">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
