<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-ef45de4a-5134-4b06-8b59-b2c887c74071'>
            
<p class="">31.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-81ac558f-d2ec-42d0-ab9a-4ce9bb195e42">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-81ac558f-d2ec-42d0-ab9a-4ce9bb195e42">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-81ac558f-d2ec-42d0-ab9a-4ce9bb195e42">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-81ac558f-d2ec-42d0-ab9a-4ce9bb195e42">
                 Mr. Riley 
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-81ac558f-d2ec-42d0-ab9a-4ce9bb195e42" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-02-07/debates/a1154570-b9d4-4f6d-bacb-02914b0941f4/MerchantShipbuildingAndRepairs#contribution-81ac558f-d2ec-42d0-ab9a-4ce9bb195e42">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the First Lord of the Admiralty whether the scheme under which the Admiralty becomes responsible as from the 1st February, 1940, for all mercantile shipbuilding and repairs will include the transfer of all shipbuilding and repair establishments to Government control and ownership; and whether the employs in such establishments will, as from the date mentioned, become Government employs?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-81ac558f-d2ec-42d0-ab9a-4ce9bb195e42" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-02-07/debates/a1154570-b9d4-4f6d-bacb-02914b0941f4/MerchantShipbuildingAndRepairs#contribution-81ac558f-d2ec-42d0-ab9a-4ce9bb195e42">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-082829a9-5403-4b24-aba6-bff32906d8df">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-082829a9-5403-4b24-aba6-bff32906d8df">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-082829a9-5403-4b24-aba6-bff32906d8df">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-082829a9-5403-4b24-aba6-bff32906d8df">
                Mr. Churchill
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-082829a9-5403-4b24-aba6-bff32906d8df" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-02-07/debates/a1154570-b9d4-4f6d-bacb-02914b0941f4/MerchantShipbuildingAndRepairs#contribution-082829a9-5403-4b24-aba6-bff32906d8df">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The answer to both parts of the Question is in the negative. There is no intention of preventing shipbuilding on private account, and the Admiralty is responsible for issuing licences for this purpose.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-082829a9-5403-4b24-aba6-bff32906d8df" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-02-07/debates/a1154570-b9d4-4f6d-bacb-02914b0941f4/MerchantShipbuildingAndRepairs#contribution-082829a9-5403-4b24-aba6-bff32906d8df">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





